string.Data: "Baidu CarLife+ is an app provided by the third-party company Baidu that provides interconnectivity between mobile devices and cars. In order to provide these interconnectivity features, this app needs to access the mobile device's Bluetooth address and location information from the car and mobile device. The app needs to connect to the internet to be able to connect to the car, update data, obtain location information, discover nearby devices and establish connections with them, and obtain the MAC address of the mobile device to calculate daily activity data. This app only requests or uses the above permissions when you use relevant features. For details, refer to the Baidu CarLife+ Terms of Service, Privacy Policy, and Service Statement."
